                  "status": "generated",
                  "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h3>Chemistry</h3><table class=\"hl7__eu__lab__report\"><thead><tr><th>Test</th><th>30-OCT-2015</th><th>Reference&#xA0;Range</th><th>Unit</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Hemoglobin A1c/Hemoglobin.total in Blood</td><td><strong>6.2 H</strong></td><td>4.8 - 5.9</td><td>%</td></tr><tr><td>Glucose [Mass/volume] in Blood</td><td>98.0</td><td>70 - 100</td><td>mg/dL</td></tr><tr><td>Urea nitrogen [Mass/volume] in Blood</td><td>18.1</td><td>7 - 20</td><td>mg/dL</td></tr><tr><td>Creatinine [Mass/volume] in Blood</td><td><strong>1.3 H</strong></td><td>0.6 - 1.2</td><td>mg/dL</td></tr><tr><td>Calcium [Mass/volume] in Blood</td><td>10.0</td><td>8.5 - 10.5</td><td>mg/dL</td></tr><tr><td>Sodium [Moles/volume] in Blood</td><td>140.1</td><td>135 - 145</td><td>mmol/L</td></tr><tr><td>Potassium [Moles/volume] in Blood</td><td>4.3</td><td>3.5 - 5.0</td><td>mmol/L</td></tr><tr><td>Chloride [Moles/volume] in Blood</td><td>102.4</td><td>98 - 107</td><td>mmol/L</td></tr><tr><td>Carbon dioxide, total [Moles/volume] in Blood</td><td>27.0</td><td>22 - 29</td><td>mmol/L</td></tr></tbody></table></div>"
